{"id":158249,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/旱苗得雨！-長江中下游黃色預警解除/","date":"2011-06-06T00:30:39Z","modified":"2011-12-28T23:38:24Z","title":"旱苗得雨！ 長江中下游黃色預警解除","content":"<p>大陸湖北、湖南等地近兩日出現降雨，大陸中央氣象台預計因部分地區還會普降甘霖，大部分乾旱地區將有不同程度緩解，因此解除長江中下游地區代表中度乾旱的黃色預警。不過，江河湖塘及水庫蓄水難有明顯增加，仍屬代表輕度乾旱的藍色預警；專家更警告，本次降雨過程累計降水較大，各地在抗旱時也須加強防汛。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://chinatimes.feedsportal.com/c/33012/f/537211/s/15a80173/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E6%97%B1%E8%8B%97%E5%BE%97%E9%9B%A8%EF%BC%81+%E9%95%B7%E6%B1%9F%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%8B%E6%B8%B8%E9%BB%83%E8%89%B2%E9%A0%90%E8%AD%A6%E8%A7%A3%E9%99%A4&amp;link=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.chinatimes.com%2Fmainland%2F11050501%2F112011060500172.html\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/06/260f6417emailthis2.gif.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E6%97%B1%E8%8B%97%E5%BE%97%E9%9B%A8%EF%BC%81+%E9%95%B7%E6%B1%9F%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%8B%E6%B8%B8%E9%BB%83%E8%89%B2%E9%A0%90%E8%AD%A6%E8%A7%A3%E9%99%A4&amp;link=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.chinatimes.com%2Fmainland%2F11050501%2F112011060500172.html\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/06/044291a1bookmark.gif.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/104471173212/u/0/f/537211/c/33012/s/15a80173/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/104471173212/u/0/f/537211/c/33012/s/15a80173/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinatimes.feedsportal.com/c/33012/f/537211/s/15a80173/mf.gif\" /></p>\n<p>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> </p>\n<p>\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[18424],"tags":[16304,15396]}